  cautionaryCompanionPatterns: []
  setupNotes: Create CombatActionDefinition assets, group them in a CombatSequenceDefinition,
    assign the sequence through a PawnCombatProfile or action system, add health
    and hitbox components, then test one hit in Play Mode.
